      "solution": "n = int(input())\ntime = n * 90 - 60\ncool_down = n // 8\nif n != 0:\n    time += cool_down * 240\n    time -= 60 * cool_down\n    if cool_down == n / 8:\n        time -= 180\n    print(time)\nelse:\n    print(0)\n",
